#. (itstool) path: sect1/para
#: tutorial-advanced.xml:47
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Paste…</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Size</guimenuitem></menuchoice> scales the whole "
"selection to match the overall size of the clipboard object(s). "
"<guimenuitem>Width</guimenuitem>/<guimenuitem>Height</guimenuitem> scale the "
